accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Office of the Secretary, Yale University, Annual Reports Submitted to the President (RU 219). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged chronologically by accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of annual reports from academic departments and programs, residential colleges, graduate and professional schools, and administrative offices of Yale University.
